Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前後屈體運動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二  三  四  五  六  七  八
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.18,0:01:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.67,0:01:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們飛上天了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.02,0:01:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.88,0:01:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三  四  五  六  七…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在……幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都叫你進來前敲門了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:03:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和紗季吵架了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季的媽媽很擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們已經不是小學生了  要馬上和好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  吃過飯之後啟太他們要來我們家玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是她不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才早上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.51,0:04:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這什麼打扮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很熱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在正和你絕交  不要隨便和我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不懂別人的好意麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那個必要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  你有沒有見到優香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看到  她一大早就不見蹤影了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子明明說暑假開始要幫家裏幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都是說說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你要來幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.77,0:05:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得把不可燃垃圾分類
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  那個  神石…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天那裏就不用打掃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會為神石打掃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能成為偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能成為讀者模特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能成為大富翁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能變得更聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望作業全部完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望不會被強迫幫家裏做事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能拿到許多零花錢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望不會變胖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望皮膚會變好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.61,0:06:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊  凜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  真多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天回去就一直在寫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果全部成真的話  我現在已經是白富美的偶像讀者模特了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不是四個人一起許願就不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  夏海和紗季她們倆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在吵架中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們倆可是相當頑固的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們能不能快點和好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果夏海和紗季和好了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一體同心 那就無敵了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們倆一體同心的話的確就無敵了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得讓她們倆快點和好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼擅自跑到別人房間裏來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是想來才來這種地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.23,0:07:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫做這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  熱死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是  給我快點離開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分不開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.03,0:08:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我放開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要壓在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全分不開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:08:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是神石？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別說傻話了  它怎麼會有這種力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們確實飛上天空了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這股力量也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說其實是你在黏著我不放
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說是有一股不可思議的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我沒有許過這種願望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是優香！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你這打扮…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要借你穿我的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你要讓我穿著內衣出去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我要說的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果什麼都沒有發生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不是四個人一起就不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們倆能夠和好就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季 發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.98,0:10:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿這雙鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是把鞋後幫踩壞了我可饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 要吃點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:10:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:10:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.75,0:11:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.90,0:11:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們不是在吵架嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼？你問這個做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大樹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟太戰隊登場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很酷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好土
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.27,0:11:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別指揮我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再向媽媽打聽一下有關神石的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這種力量要是告訴別人就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能旁敲側擊地打聽出來倒是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是凜的媽媽直覺很敏銳啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.75,0:12:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我試試看去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫到這裏就可以麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今天就到這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們去買冰淇淋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香不用幫家裏做事麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就偷一次懶了 這大熱天的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黏在一起了耶 和好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是感覺好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香 我們逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別一下子前進
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要前進了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香 凜子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:12:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別逃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 為什麼這麼生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她們黏在一起了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黏在了一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個啦 因為神石
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不明白嗎 因為她們心虛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼會明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是明擺著的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.84,0:13:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.93,0:14:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海？ 紗季？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫著走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們果然黏在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我和凜許願了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一定要四個人一起許願才行的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人許的願也會實現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定藏在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:14:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不告訴我你要搬家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在說那個幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很重要的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們約定好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不都說了沒和你定下什麼約定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.43,0:15:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.62,0:15:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.50,0:15:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們非常生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換成是你和我黏在一起分不開的話 你也會生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 往這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明還差一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.74,0:16:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.08,0:16:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是盯著看的時候啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是這樣 是吧 祐介
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 昨天我從山裏的秘密基地看天空的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有四個女的在空中飛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且肯定是大樹的姐姐她們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.91,0:16:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的像是飛起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.93,0:16:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是那種飛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香 往這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:17:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:18:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想想辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼知道怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太頑強了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.99,0:18:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣太危險了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底幹了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香她？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:19:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說你們要是一體同心的話那就無敵了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她為什麼跑到那裏去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她跑得太累了 根本沒看前面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下 優香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香說你們要是一體同心那就無敵了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和紗季是無敵的？ 這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是理所當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓優香停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.94,0:19:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們左右包抄她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.37,0:20:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你們和好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說我和夏海有了同樣的想法和心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以優香她們許的願就被解除了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和紗季…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.28,0:20:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我才該說對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.72,0:21:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季 下週一開始的社團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一起打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.43,0:21:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有什麼目標和夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想和紗季一起打網球而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她絕對沒有在反省
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.73,0:21:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們到神石那裏去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.11,0:21:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 四個人一起許願的話就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.37,0:21:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們四個人一起去許願吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四個人能一起成為偶像什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你睡什麼覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要睡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要睡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜也睡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.84,0:21:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們睡什麼覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要出席太鼓祭的歌手大會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得優勝 然後去試鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.03,0:21:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在聽嗎 明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:22:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（收信人：逢澤夏海    對不起）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.32,0:23:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（世界魔女大全）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.49,0:23:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次可被優香給害慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.70,0:24:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上起床發現自己成了偶像怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.26,0:24:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話也就只能…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.38,0:24:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就沒關係嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.07,0:24:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果一定要許願的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.85,0:24:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就許個一般來說一定不會實現的願望比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.54,0:24:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.23,0:24:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如能聽懂貓說的話什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.81,0:24:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季還真是意外的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.73,0:24:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算 剛才說的不算
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.60,0:24:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 夏色奇跡 第三話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.11,0:24:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下田的天空有時會有少女飛過
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.57,0:24:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 紗季喵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.89,0:24:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在空中飛的時候好像被別人看到了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.42,0:24:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要喵
